        public Bullet(int x,
              int y,
              int destX,
              int destY,
              Weapon currentWeapon)
        A constructor for a bullet. It needs the current weapon and coordinates of the shooter and the destination to work.
        Parameters:
        x - X-Coordinate of the shooter.
        y - Y-Coordinate of the shooter.
        destX - X-Coordinate of the target.
        destY - Y-Coordinate of the target.
        currentWeapon - Weapon of use.
